==============================================================================

CHANGES IN VERSION 0.03


    - Updated Makefile.PL to note Perl6::Export 0.07 dependency

	- Added correct behaviour when no source specified


==============================================================================

AVAILABILITY

Perl6::Slurp has been uploaded to the CPAN

